  "subject": "Replace jenkins verify/merge jobs build node with the one contains docker",
  "commit_message": "Replace jenkins verify/merge jobs build node with the one contains docker\n\nCurrent jenkins verify/merge jobs do not need docker to run tests, but\nintegration tests with testcontainer (https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/aai/traversal/+/121141)\nneed docker to run successfully.\n\nIssue-ID: AAI-3325\nSigned-off-by: Mohammad Hosnidokht <mohammad.hosnidokht@yoppworks.com>\nChange-Id: I0b97e026b8e08e591d150cc1b34eddd20ee5123c\n",
